🔎 Issues in your current settings
SECRET_KEY is hardcoded

In production, you shouldn’t keep it in the repo.

Heroku expects it in an environment variable, e.g. SECRET_KEY.

ALLOWED_HOSTS

Currently you only allow 127.0.0.1 and *.herokuapp.com.

But your app URL is practice-my-blog-fd3393450c3b.herokuapp.com, which is fine.

